data.title: Which team originally drafted 2010-11 Suns forward Channing Frye?
data.text:
Which NBA player made 103 successful 3-point shots during his 2010-11 rookie season?

Basketball Trivia / July 20, 2024

Wesley Johnson. Wesley Johnson averaged 9 points per game during his rookie year with the Timberwolves.

What is the Chris Bosh Foundation set up to promote?

Basketball Trivia / July 20, 2024

Sports And Education. The Chris Bosh Foundation promotes education and sports in youth of Dallas and Toronto.

Who coached the Nets right after Willis Reed moved up to VP of basketball operations?

Basketball Trivia / July 19, 2024

Bill Fitch. Nets first season with Fitch as coach they won only 17 games.

What is the name of Yao Ming's mother?

Basketball Trivia / July 19, 2024

Fang Feng Di. Both of Yao Ming's parents played for Chinese national basketball teams.

What year did Tony Parker enter the NBA draft?

Basketball Trivia / July 18, 2024

2001. Tony Parker played professional basketball in France before entering the NBA Draft in 2001.
